{
  "stem": "23090.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My grandfather was a clarinetist in the Lodz Symphony Orchestra.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my great-grandfather was a flutist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my uncles, they played all instruments, from violins, to drums, to-- to the percussion-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the trombones and the various instruments.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know and I can't recall any one of my members of my family that either didn't sing or play or perform in some capacity as an entertainer, both in the Yiddish theater in our community and, of course, outside the Yiddish theater, more formal performing.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I'm basically-- I come from a generation or from a-- from a background, a musical background.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I don't also recall the time where you'd come to my house that there wasn't someone playing something, either practicing some-- some future concert or just fiddling around, as the expression is.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we just grew up in that environment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was my desire to be the-- to do the same and wanting to be a musician and a concert pianist, of which, unfortunately, I wasn't given the opportunity, as a result of the war.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I led a-- as I say, a very normal life as a child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was a housewife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and-- as much as I-- as much as you remember your mother, I remember my mother as the most loving mother, as any child would, and one who I can honestly tell you, I don't remember what she looked like.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Perhaps it's just a-- one of those things that you erase out of your mind, but something you just hold very dear to your heart in just a special place, and very sacred.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
